::'''Doremem:''' Oh, manager, mem. What can I get for you?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Just dropping by to see how everyone's doing.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Has work been going well lately?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504131505-->
::'''Doremem:''' Thank you for asking, manager, mem. Being a server here, carrying piping-hot dishes and enjoying unlimited staff meals every day, has been my dream since I was little, mem.
::'''Doremem:''' Though after actually becoming a server, I realized the restaurant stays open really late. By the end of each day, my smile feels frozen in place, and I'm often too busy to even eat the staff meal...
::'''Doremem:''' But when I bring a delicious dish to a customer and see them smile, somehow my face doesn't feel sore anymore, my stomach stops growling, and all the exhaustion just fades away, mem!
::'''Doremem:''' Um, manager, a guest just arrived. I should go greet them, mem.
::'''Doremem:''' Come one, come all! Take a look, memi! Step right up, step right in, come and taste it, memi!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
