::'''Doremem:''' Come one, come all! Take a look, memi! Step right up, step right in, come and taste it, memi!
::'''Doremem:''' Welcome, dear guest! What would you like to order today?
::'''Doremem:''' Candied Quillorb Berries, Quillorb Fruit Brew, Oven-Baked Quillorb Berry Pie, Quillorb Salad, Quillorb Berry Jam &mdash; we've got it all, memi! Please, take your pick!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why is it all Quillorbs?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Quillorbs it is, then.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504115306-->
::'''Doremem:''' Sorry, memi. Truth is, we don't even have any Quillorbs. I was just practicing my restaurant service lines.
::'''Doremem:''' Even though the restaurants in the Maze have long been closed, I've always dreamed of being a server, memi! Carrying hot dishes fresh from the kitchen, unlimited staff meals every day &mdash; that must be the best job in the world, memi!
::'''Doremem:''' I&mdash;I even think I was born for it, memi!
::'''Doremem:''' But before that... I need to practice, and practice hard.
::'''Doremem:''' "Come one, come all! Take a look, memi! Step right up, come and try it, memi!"
